title: A Quick Note from QLS
itunes:title: A Quick Note from QLS
description:
Hey QLS fam. We are taking two weeks to self-care and record some new Questlove Supreme interviews. Stay tuned for our return on September 21. We will continue re-releasing QLS Classics in the meantime, and make sure you check out our vast archives.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
